    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-6 w-full max-w-7xl">
      
      <%= link_to "https://voyageutah.com/interview/inspiring-conversations-with-madeleine-elizabeth-chuy-allende-of-just-a-craving/?fbclid=IwQ0xDSwKtempleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHuRQnteJMeVScT1_pVtB_cWNxVj6VXh-e18qMJXsC251uMW31Sb8qbyiR-Xe_aem_eqL5jFwYfAarE83Ex37lpQ", target: "_blank" do %>
        <%= image_tag "news2.png", class: "w-70 rounded-lg shadow-lg hidden lg:block" %>
      <% end %>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 max-w-3xl bg-gray-600/20 rounded-lg">
        <div class="mx-3 my-3">
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold text-amber-300">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-md text-gray-50 max-w-2xl">
          We are a Utah local business. We started in Bountiful with a Food Truck, selling food cravings such as Philly Cheese Steaks, Soups, Tamales, and so much more. We started in the Fall, but when the Winter hit, we realized it was very hard to stay warm. So we started thinking about cravings for the Summer. We wanted something different, delicious, & refreshing. Presentation, flavor and quality  has always been our main focus. As a result, My partner and I, thought about what we and our families enjoy the most in the summer, and that was Shaved ice.
